<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tax Return Processed - Taxmind</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        body,
        table,
        td,
        p,
        a,
        li,
        blockquote {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }

        table,
        td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }

        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .banner {
            width: 100%;
            background-size: cover !important;
            background-position: center !important;
            background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
            height: 80px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 0 48px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 19px 0;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #5f5f5f;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            margin: 19px 0;
        }

        .name {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #000000;
        }

        .instructions {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #5f5f5f;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 19px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #01afed;
            padding: 16px 48px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }

        .contact-divider {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 1px;
            height: 19px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            opacity: 0.5;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .summary-box {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-left: 4px solid #1a73e9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #1a73e9;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
            .content {
                padding: 0 24px !important;
            }

            .footer {
                padding: 16px 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div
        style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="banner"
            style="background-image: url('https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/banner_image.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 80px;">
            <tr>
                <td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 31px 0 0 48px;">
                    <img src="https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/logo.png" alt="Taxmind Logo"
                        style="width: 119px; height: 29px; display: block;">
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <img src="https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/tick_block.png" alt="Success"
                        style="display:inline-block; margin: 18px 0 0 0; height: 60px;">
                    <h1 class="title">Your Tax Return is Ready</h1>
                    <p class="greeting">Hi <span class="name">{{name}}</span> 👋</p>
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <p>We have successfully processed your tax return for {{year}}. A summary of your return is
                            provided below:</p>

                        <div class="summary-box">
                            {{{summary}}}
                        </div>

                        <p>You can now view the masked version of your tax document in your dashboard.</p>

                        {{#if paymentUrl}}
                        <p>To finalize the process, please complete the pending payment using the button below:</p>
                        <a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="cta-button">Pay Now</a>
                        {{/if}}

                        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
                        <p>Regards,<br>Team Taxmind</p>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td align="center" valign="middle" class="contact-info"
                                style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; vertical-align: middle;">
                                <span>+353 871986494</span>
                                <span class="contact-divider"></span>
                                <span>info@taxmind.ie</span>
                                <span class="contact-divider"></span>
                                <img src="https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/X.png" alt="Twitter"
                                    class="social-icon" style="margin: 0 5px; vertical-align: middle;">
                                <img src="https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/facebook.png"
                                    alt="Facebook" class="social-icon" style="margin: 0 5px; vertical-align: middle;">
                                <img src="https://taxmind-dev-public.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/instagram.png"
                                    alt="Instagram" class="social-icon" style="margin: 0 5px; vertical-align: middle;">
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>

</html>